<view class="container">
  <view class="mesh-gradient"></view>
  <navbar title="个人资料" showBack="{{true}}"></navbar>

  <view class="main-body px-4 pt-4">
    <view class="glass-card p-6 rounded-2xl mb-6">
        <view class="form-group mb-4">
            <text class="label block text-sm font-bold text-slate-700 mb-2">姓名 <text class="text-red-500">*</text></text>
            <input class="input-field w-full p-3 bg-white/50 rounded-xl border border-white" placeholder="请输入您的称呼" value="{{formData.name}}" bindinput="onInput" data-field="name"/>
        </view>

        <view class="form-group mb-4">
            <text class="label block text-sm font-bold text-slate-700 mb-2">联系电话 <text class="text-red-500">*</text></text>
            <input class="input-field w-full p-3 bg-white/50 rounded-xl border border-white" type="number" placeholder="销售将通过此号码联系您" value="{{formData.phone}}" bindinput="onInput" data-field="phone"/>
        </view>

        <view class="form-group mb-4">
            <text class="label block text-sm font-bold text-slate-700 mb-2">微信号 (选填)</text>
            <input class="input-field w-full p-3 bg-white/50 rounded-xl border border-white" placeholder="便于微信沟通" value="{{formData.wechat}}" bindinput="onInput" data-field="wechat"/>
        </view>
    </view>

    <view class="text-xs text-muted text-center mb-6 px-4">
        * 完善资料后，您的房源将能被系统中的销售顾问看到并推荐给租客。
    </view>

    <button class="w-full bg-primary text-white py-3 rounded-xl font-bold shadow-lg shadow-primary-20 icon-hover-bounce" bindtap="onSave">保存资料</button>
  </view>
</view>
